title: For Sale:  S&W 3914 with lots of extras (mags, ammo, holsters)
postcontent:
As some of you are probably well aware, most gun experts have definitively stated that the S&W 3913/3914 family of lightweight compact pistols are probably the best 9mm pistols one can use for CCW.

These pistols are accurate and super reliable. Easily as reliable as a Glock 26.

The 3913 is the most commonly seen version, and is available in LS, NL, and TSW configurations. The 3914 is the black version most popular with LE, and many who have owned both have stated that the trigger on the 3914 is smoother and accuracy was better. The 908 was the economy version that was released a few years later and not up to the same standards. Thus, the 3914 is the best 9mm pistol S&W has ever made or ever will make. These early pistols have no lock and no MIM parts. You cannot find a better 9mm CCW pistol anywhere.

These pistols have an alloy frame which can withstand +P ammo. They weight only 24 oz. 8+1 capacity. DA/SA with ambi decocker. Shaved hammer is flush with the slide. Mine has had less than 150 rounds down the pipe and is in like new condition. Beautiful pistol.

The negatives? Very few. It is a 9 shot 9mm and you cannot get wood aftermarket grips for it. Those are the negatives. The only reason I am selling this is to fund another purchase, because while I intended this to be my CCW it never gets carried, and I want something bigger for my nightstand gun.

S&W 3914
4 factory 8 rd mags
83 rds of Remington Golden Saber +P
50 rds pf Remington Golden Saber
12 rds Federal Guard Dog
100 rds Federal AE 124 gr FMJ
Brand new Galco tuckable IWB holster (RH)
Brand new Bianchi IWB holster (LH/SOB)
cheap RH IWB holster
extra base plates for mags.

This is complete package. I am finally stepping away from this caliber.

$550 CASH takes everything. This is really a great deal. Golden Saber ammo is the best you can buy and goes for a buck a round. Holsters are brand new. Extra mags are over 30 each when you can find them. Do the math.  Do not have original box or manual.  Not interested in trades.  Will not ship.  Legal CO buyers only.

File photo attached.
